    <string name="instructions_title">How to Use</string>
<string name="instructions_step1_title"><b>1. Import eBook, then Audiobook:</b></string>
<string name="instructions_step1_line1">Open the app and tap on the Import (+) button.</string>
<string name="instructions_step1_line2">Select a .epub file (<b>eBook must be selected FIRST</b>) and then when you open it, select the corresponding audiobook from your device storage.</string>

<string name="instructions_step2_title"><b>2. Start The Audiobook at your desired Position:</b></string>
<string name="instructions_step2_line1">Go to the position of the EPUB that corresponds to the Audiobook</string>
<string name="instructions_step2_line2">Tap on the Anchor button to start transcribing the audiobook and anchor the audio to the text.</string>
<string name="instructions_step2_line3">The app will process the audio and move the EPUB with the corresponding text in the book.</string>
<string name="instructions_step2_line4">Once transcription is complete, the app will automatically sync the text with the eBook.</string>
<string name="instructions_step2_line5">You can now switch between listening and reading seamlessly.</string>

<string name="instructions_step3_title"><b>3. Read and Listen:</b></string>
<string name="instructions_step3_line1">Use the built-in reader to read the eBook while listening to the audiobook.</string>
<string name="instructions_step3_line2">The app will highlight the text as the audio plays for a synchronized experience.</string>

